sql: SELECT COURSEalias0.DEPARTMENT , COURSEalias0.NAME , COURSEalias0.NUMBER FROM COURSE AS COURSEalias0 WHERE COURSEalias0.ENFORCED_REQUIREMENT = "N / A" AND LOWER( COURSEalias0.DESCRIPTION ) LIKE "%artificial intelligence%" ;
